[6] New countries confirming imported cases -- Australia, Nepal, France, Malaysia
- Australia ex China
Date: Sat 25 Jan 2020
Source: Herald Sun [abridged, edited]
https://www.heraldsun.com.au/news/victoria/victorian-case-of-coronavirus-confirmed/news-story/3ff9db31c99434df33720c9f74417885?utm_content=SocialFlow&utm_medium=Twitter&utm_campaign=EditorialSF&utm_source=HeraldSun


A case of the deadly coronavirus has been confirmed in Victoria. The Sunday Herald Sun has learned the person returned to Melbourne from Wuhan in China last week. The State Government will make the announcement today [25 Jan 2020].

The recent outbreak of coronavirus China has quickly spread to other parts of the world.

[Byline: Tom Minear and Rebekah Cavanagh]

